query:
SELECT
"sr_customer_sk" "ctr_customer_sk"
, "sr_store_sk" "ctr_store_sk"
, "sum"("sr_return_amt") "ctr_total_return"
FROM
store_returns
, date_dim
WHERE ("sr_returned_date_sk" = "d_date_sk")
AND ("d_year" = 2000)
GROUP BY "sr_customer_sk", "sr_store_sk"
